Package edu.phema.elm_to_omop.api

Class ElmToOmopTranslator

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.phema.elm_to_omop.api.ElmToOmopTranslator
  • public class ElmToOmopTranslator
extends Object
    Provides methods for converting a CQL string to OMOP WebAPI requests using the functionality implemented in this library.
